Package: orthoRibbon
Type: Package
Title: Ribbon-Diagram Visualization of Orthologous Genes Across Species
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given="Jianhong", family="Ou", email="jou@morgridge.org", 
        role=c("aut", "cre"), comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-8652-2488")),
        person(given='Kenneth', family='Poss', email='kposs@morgridge.org',
        role=c('aut', 'fnd')))
Description: OrthoRibbon is a visualization toolkit for displaying orthologous
    gene relationships across species using ribbon-based diagrams.
    It enables intuitive comparison of conserved genes and genomic
    correspondence between chromosomes or genomic regions.
    The package supports flexible input formats and produces publication-quality
    figures for comparative genomics and evolutionary analysis.
